                    <span>A very clear book applying SPIN Selling techniques. No fluff, no extraneous threads leading you away from the primary focus. The techniques can be applied far beyond sales, and utilized in a broader sense to persuade as opposed to the narrower definition of selling.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Great Book</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
